OL,5, Two million people could have their gas
OL,6, and electricity cut off this winter    
OL,7, because they cannot afford to top up   
OL,8, their prepayment meter, new research   
OL,9, suggests.                              
OL,11,FCitizens Advice has warned that having 
OL,12,Fno gas and electricity would not be a  
OL,13,F"one-off" experience for many.         
OL,15,FIt comes as a separate report suggests 
OL,16,Fmillions are living far below the      
OL,17,Fpoverty line in the UK.                
OL,19,FThe government said it is spending     
OL,20,Fbillions on supporting households.     
